{"tid":2456703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"科興打吾打得過?","createTime":"2021-03-22T06:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T07:56:56.000Z","uid":358141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"866f1270f7afc5933685128e3e8b8852f167944a","tid":2456703,"uid":358141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"拿，應該甘計:<br />\n1) 如果吾打疫苗<br />\n   風險 = 中招風險 x 死亡率<br />\n   1.1 中招風險:  好難估, 但以2009年的H1N1大流行為例, 有研究顯示至今感染左全球10-20%人口。就當是有10%機會始終會中招  [資料1]<br />\n   1.2 死亡率: 官方數字是1%, 但這個數字是未計算中左都吾知果D隱形傳播者。我就當隱形傳播佔了總傳播量的九成。即係實制死亡率系 0.01 x 0.1 = 0.001.<br />\n  ==&gt; 所以, 如果吾打, 風險系 0.1*0.001 = 0.0001<br />\n<br />\n2) 如果打科興<br />\n   風險 = 因疫苗而死風險 +  疫苗無效而肺炎而死風險<br />\n2.1 因疫苗而死:  20萬人打, 當死10個。風險 10/200000 = 0.00005<br />\n2.2 疫苗無效而肺炎而死:我就當科星保護率真的有50%, 所以, 死亡率是上面無打的一半, 即係 0.0001 x 0 .5 = 0.00005<br />\n==&gt; 所以, 如果打科興, 總風險係  0.00005+ 0.00005 = 0.0001<br />\n<br />\n<strong>0.0001 比 0.0001 !! 打和 !!!</strong>  <br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料1 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2009_swine_flu_pandemic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2009_swine_flu_pandemic&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=d5cbdacb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2009_swine_flu_pandemic</a>"},{"pid":"6e167002e09f7cd0589fa084877c8642abfe46ab","tid":2456703,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"打德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632eb3b3accd07670d0c003c2a8dd962cc038f8a","tid":2456703,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"吾系甘計牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc895d22d720186e03f5a2880af1814dd899dab","tid":2456703,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"溝針?"},{"pid":"0a21035667080a8b3aea39d3ed49b9293024f19a","tid":2456703,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"用晒成副身家買份人壽寫女神名再去打無得輸，死唔去就拎埋份保險同女神示愛，死撚咗就一大舊錢俾女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62773c997457bf3d414eaa2cc392ee5a2767cda","tid":2456703,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"吾打吾打, 即係你會打啦"},{"pid":"7823c65323623469799c765cf9825bba06ffb937","tid":2456703,"uid":360907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:56:56.000Z","msg":"得一年有效<br />\n每年同佢對賭一次<br />\n計埋入去未？"}]}